channel.title: The "MoparScape 3.2" decompiled files WITHIN THE .Jar? (plus a bit more)
channel.description:
Alright. Um, I know this is mostly a big request, but I would like to ask anyways. Could anyone give me the decompiled files of these posted here? (so I can actually compile them) I would use a program or something, but DIAL UP TAKES FOREVER TO DOWNLOAD...

And just a few froms from the "Hybirdscape" folder... - NPCHandler - Shop handler - Client Handler
And I noticed, I used a decompiling program in the past, and when I tried to recompile, the .bat said the "100 errors" part, so yea...
